Usage: sort_collection [-help] <collection> <property_or_list_of_properties>
                       [-descending] [-dictionary]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
<collection>                         # Collection to sort (string, required)
<property_or_list_of_properties>     # Sorts the collection by the specified
                                     # property (string, required)
-descending                          # Sorts the objects in the collection by
                                     # descending order (bool, optional)
-dictionary                          # Sorts the objects in the collection by
                                     # dictionary order (bool, optional)